{"tid":1607061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎睇一睇 咁多人跑個陣跌低係因為無肌肉記憶","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:52:48.000Z","uid":131259,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"452ef4a9580300e1a3b132804475bc13702e9f7e","tid":1607061,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"肌肉記憶簡單d講就係「先前累積既訓練經驗，讓過程變得更有效率，知道該如何控制身體行動；使肌肉收縮、聚集肌纖維。」<br />\n<br />\n試諗下當要全速跑個陣 成世人你有幾何試過唔係由一個<span style=\"color: red;\">準備姿勢</span>去發動<br />\n係d好驚慌好急既情況之下 正正你就係要係各種唔就腳既情況下去發動<br />\n可能係雙腳直立緊 可能係俟緊欄杆 可能係突然要轉身跑<br />\n事先無演練過 係依D情況下拔足狂奔一定好大機會腳軟仆街<br />\n所以你地班友唔該搵機會預演下各種情況 <span style=\"color: red;\">意識同身體上都做個準備</span><br />\n<br />\n真實例子可以睇下上年Tai Po比人斬個條友 因為驚第一步就自己仆低左<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fMQpmW4Ppjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfMQpmW4Ppjk&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=28a4cb68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fMQpmW4Ppjk</a><br />\n<br />\n利申: 絕對反對任何非法行為，純學術討論"},{"pid":"2d56d07638d541992f55a213d78e1b9faa7f8fc0","tid":1607061,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92078e2b62e7bd530718b744c2a009a9e1019cec","tid":1607061,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ec193b78654c95f57f1b992256f86244462a23","tid":1607061,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edf7b1fbb63d07b6aab6bc915669d7f0ff84e98","tid":1607061,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"